summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting an agreement and easement for the repair of a retaining wall on McGilvra Boulevard East in Tract 159, Replat of John J. McGilvra's Addition to the City of Seattle and Blocks 13, 14, 18, 20 to 29, inclusive, and South Half of 19 of John J. McGilvra's Second Addition to the City of Seattle (McGilvra Boulevard Retaining Wall; RW 8703).
